  "title": "chore: Add Usage Trend of InstantSearch Family",
  "body": "I’d like to suggest adding a link to the README that shows the usage trend of the InstantSearch family of packages. This link will direct users to a dynamic chart that visualizes the download trends of related packages over the past three years, helping new users evaluate the popularity and adoption of InstantSearch tools.\r\n\r\nAs a maintainer of npm-compare.com, I’m also happy to implement any other features that could benefit your project, if you find them useful.\r\n\r\nThanks for considering my suggestion!",
